Description.SourceString: 沃兰雪原居民常用的武器，根据地域特点增加了寒冰属性。平价而高效，广受欢迎。
Description.LocalizedString: A common weapon among residents of Warren Snowfield. Infused with frost to reflect the local flavor. It's very popular, because it's cheap yet highly effective.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 沃兰雪原居民常用的武器，根据地域特点增加了寒冰属性。平价而高效，广受欢迎。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A common weapon among residents of Warren Snowfield. Infused with frost to reflect the local flavor. It's very popular, because it's cheap yet highly effective.

Description.SourceString: 班吉斯重工研发的基础型武器，使用特制合金制作，轻便而灵活，打击感十足。
Description.LocalizedString: A basic weapon developed by Banges Tech. Forged in a special alloy, it is light, agile, and easy to handle.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 班吉斯重工研发的基础型武器，使用特制合金制作，轻便而灵活，打击感十足。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A basic weapon developed by Banges Tech. Forged in a special alloy, it is light, agile, and easy to handle.

Description.SourceString: 最早被立项的电能原能武具项目，上手简单，受到许多不擅长战斗的拓荒者的欢迎。
Description.LocalizedString: The earliest electromagnetic Omnium project. The blade is easy to handle, and is very popular among Wanderers that are not great fighters.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 最早被立项的电能原能武具项目，上手简单，受到许多不擅长战斗的拓荒者的欢迎。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: The earliest electromagnetic Omnium project. The blade is easy to handle, and is very popular among Wanderers that are not great fighters.

Description.SourceString: 雪原上的猎人常用的武器，能够轻松命中猎物。经过推广后，现已在平价民用市场占据半壁江山。
Description.LocalizedString: A popular snowfield hunting weapon, easy to handle with high accuracy. Widely promoted, it now dominates over half the civilian market.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 雪原上的猎人常用的武器，能够轻松命中猎物。经过推广后，现已在平价民用市场占据半壁江山。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A popular snowfield hunting weapon, easy to handle with high accuracy. Widely promoted, it now dominates over half the civilian market.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增强圣痕权杖治疗能力，4件套进一步辅助增伤
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the healing of Staff of Scars. The four-set bonus further supports increased damage.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，从而增强治疗能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases weapon charge, which enhances healing.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，从而增强治疗能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases weapon charge, which enhances healing.

Description.SourceString: 刻有十字圣符的机械法杖，或宽恕己罪或降临神罚。
Description.LocalizedString: A mechanical staff with a cross rune carved into it. Capable of both forgiving sins or unleashing punishments.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 刻有十字圣符的机械法杖，或宽恕己罪或降临神罚。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A mechanical staff with a cross rune carved into it. Capable of both forgiving sins or unleashing punishments.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合终结者射程
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits The Terminator's range.

Description.SourceString: 火器界超越枪炮史的绝命之作，人称移动炮台的重型机枪。
Description.LocalizedString: The most gnarly firearm ever created, also known as a moving turret.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 火器界超越枪炮史的绝命之作，人称移动炮台的重型机枪。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: The most gnarly firearm ever created, also known as a moving turret.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合初动重击的蓄力重击
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits the Focus Smash of Pummeler.

Description.SourceString: 面对这样的大锤，应该没有人会想要迎面接下它的沉重敲击。
Description.LocalizedString: No one wants to be on the receiving end of this maul.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 面对这样的大锤，应该没有人会想要迎面接下它的沉重敲击。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: No one wants to be on the receiving end of this maul.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高夜雀之羽伤害，契合其重伤特质
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the damage of Nightingale's Feather and benefits its grievous trait.

Description.SourceString: 犹如暗夜般的弓矢，可以完美地融入幽邃的夜色。
Description.LocalizedString: Blends perfectly into the gloomy night.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 犹如暗夜般的弓矢，可以完美地融入幽邃的夜色。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: Blends perfectly into the gloomy night.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高武器充能值，增加雷霆战戟连携技释放频率
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the weapon charge and the frequency of Thunderous Halberd discharge skill use.

Description.SourceString: 被灌注了雷霆之力的长枪，爆发力超高，兼顾近远攻守。
Description.LocalizedString: A halberd infused with the power of thunder. Great for burst damage, and its length makes it a great weapon for a variety of ranges.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 被灌注了雷霆之力的长枪，爆发力超高，兼顾近远攻守。

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: Dual EM Stars dish out a large number of attacks, able to obtain the two-set bonus and maximize the four-set bonus.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高空中输出能力，4件套大幅提高辅助增益
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases aerial damage output. The four-set bonus significantly improves support buffs.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合超电磁双星的攻击距离
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits the attack range of Dual EM Stars.

进阶后，暴击越高破盾能力越强
适合搭配暴击暴伤装备

Excels at damage output and Shatter. <blue>Hold Energy Burst</> to increase <blue>Crit</>.
 Increases Shatter with Crit upon advancement.
 Recommended for equipment providing high Crit and Crit Damage.

Description.SourceString: 参考磁轨炮原理制作而成枪械，需要成对使用。
Description.LocalizedString: These firearms are designed based on railguns, and must be used in a pair.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>普攻伤害</>型武器，闪攻可提升自身<blue>暴击</>
进阶后，从敌人背后攻击可获得<blue>暴击暴伤</>加成
适合搭配普攻增伤型武器，以及暴击暴伤装备
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Normal Attack Damage</> weapon. Increases <blue>Crit</> with Dodge Attack.
 Grants <blue>Crit and Crit Damage</> boosts while attacking from behind upon advancement.
 Recommended for weapons with Normal Attack damage boosts and equipment providing high Crit and Crit Damage.

Description.SourceString: 如同小丑先生的各种魔术小刀一样，变幻莫测如影随形且致命无声。
Description.LocalizedString: Lethal, unpredictable and quiet.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 大灾变前最后一款原能匕首，堆砌了当时最顶尖的技术成果，产量极低，图纸被民间寻到后复刻而成。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: The latest Omnium dagger model in the pre-Cataclysm era, which features the most cutting-edge technologies back then. Very rare. Replicated according to the blueprint leaked to the public.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the damage output of Guren Blade in the air. The four-set bonus increases the duration of the damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套契合红莲刃多段攻击，缩短武器技能cd
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus benefits the multi-attack of Guren Blade, shortening weapon skill CD.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套和4件套契合红莲刃的多段攻击，提高输出能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus and the four-set bonus benefit the multi-attack of Guren Blade, increasing damage output.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高对重伤目标的伤害，契合红莲刃的物理属性
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the damage dealt with the grievous targets and fits the Physical stat of Guren Blade.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
技能对单体敌人伤害较高
进阶后，可获得强大的<blue>增伤</>效果，且对<blue>技能伤害</>的增伤尤为显著
适合搭配技能伤害高的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Skills deal high damage against single targets.
 Grants greater <blue>damage boosts</>, especially to <blue>skill damage</>, upon advancement.
 Recommended for weapons dealing high Skill Damage.

Description.SourceString: 利刃的剑锋是正义的代行者，红莲的剑身象征着勇敢坚毅的品格。
Description.LocalizedString: The crimson blade stands for courage and resolve, while the sharp edge carries out justice.

LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: The whip favored by the new Executor, Umi. Umi's favorite part of it is that she doesn't get tripped up by it, usually.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高护盾存在覆盖率，4件套辅助全队增伤
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases shield duration and coverage, and the four-set bonus increases the damage output of the team.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，提高辅助能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the charge of weapons and increases the support effectiveness.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
技能和连携兼具<blue>生存</>和<blue>恢复</>能力，<blue>空中攻击-原能飞弹</>还可限制敌人的恢复能力
进阶后，还可获得一定<blue>辅助增伤</>能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Skills and Discharge Skills provide both <blue>survivability</> and <blue>healing</>. <blue>Omnium Missile</> can also interrupts enemies from healing.
 Grants <blue>Damage Boost Support</> upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 似乎魔方的使用者总能想出各种方法来否定不必要的条件。
Description.LocalizedString: Users of the Strange Cube tend to think of many ways to negate unnecessary requirements.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 似乎魔方的使用者总能想出各种方法来否定不必要的条件。

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高容错率，4件套提供持续续航能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases fault tolerance. The four-set bonus increases sustainability.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增加护盾存在覆盖率，4件套辅助全队增伤
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases shield duration and coverage, and the four-set bonus increases the damage output of the team.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加切换到蔷薇之锋之后的反伤能力，切走时辅助下一把武器
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage reflection after switching to Rosy Edge, also supports the next switched weapon.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
技能可提供大量<blue>抗性加成</>，连携附带<blue>护盾</>效果
进阶后，破盾敌人可恢复自身生命
尤其擅长对抗冰系攻击的敌人
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Skills provide lots of <blue>Resistance boosts</> and Discharge Skills provide <blue>Shield</> effects.
Restores HP when shattering enemies after advancement.
Especially effective against Frost-type enemies.

Description.SourceString: 高贵优雅的冰霜巨剑，仿佛傲立于峭峰雪岭的纯白之花。
Description.LocalizedString: An elegant frost blade that conjures up images of a pure white flower blooming on a snow-covered cliff.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 高贵优雅的冰霜巨剑，仿佛傲立于峭峰雪岭的纯白之花。

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 提供暴击伤害契合格莱普尼的6阶暴击率提升并拥有不错的后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: Provide crit damage to match Gleipnir's R6 crit rate increase, and come with good off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果搭配雷队也可以使用天琅意志获得很好的后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: When in a volt group, use Tian Lang's matrix to get powerful off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果搭配影织也可能使用凛夜意志来获得后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: When paired with Shadoweave, use Lin's matrix to get off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果没有更好的意志选择也可以临时使用该意志
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: If there are no better matrices, use this one for now.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
充能速度快，连续的普攻可使目标进入<blue>沉醉状态</>，进而自身获得<blue>增伤</>能力
进阶后，可获得显著的<blue>连携增伤</>效果
适合搭配连携伤害高的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Charges fast. Consecutive Normal Attacks <blue>intoxicate</> targets and grant <blue>damage boosts</>.
 Grants effective <blue>Discharge Damage Boost</> upon advancement.
 Recommended for weapons dealing high Discharge Damage.

Description.SourceString: 能够将声波置换成攻击力量的特殊装置，当枷锁被释放，死亡电流将化作利爪，撕裂一切。
Description.LocalizedString: A special device that converts sound waves into attack. When the shackles are shattered, the currents of death become sharp claws that tear everything apart.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 能够将声波置换成攻击力量的特殊装置，当枷锁被释放，死亡电流将化作利爪，撕裂一切。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A special device that converts sound waves into attack. When the shackles are shattered, the currents of death become sharp claws that tear everything apart.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增加治疗的收益，提高输出，4件套进一步通过治疗来产生额外输出
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases healing and damage output. The four-set bonus further dishes out extra damage output via healing.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，从而增强治疗能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases weapon charge, which enhances healing.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:

Description.SourceString: 设计者不明，原型蓝图已流失的特制悬浮电磁炮，内部有独特的电气储蓄工艺，一旦用坏维修起来极其麻烦，但班吉斯重工的钴蓝似乎能做到。
Description.LocalizedString: Its designer is unknown. The special hovering EM Blaster's prototype's blueprint has been lost. It contains a unique electrical saving process in its interior. It's extremely troublesome to repair when it gets worn out, but Cobalt-B of Banges Tech seems to be able to do it.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套和4件套契合环刃的武器技能爆发
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set and four-set bonuses benefit the chakram's weapon skill bursts.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套和4件套契合环刃的高频伤害，大幅提高输出
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set and four-set bonuses benefit the high damage frequency of the chakram and significantly increases damage output.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
普攻分支和技能适合应对群体敌人
进阶后，释放技能后可获得<blue>短暂强力增伤</>效果，适合搭配高爆发的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Normal Attack Branch and Skills are effective against groups of enemies.
 Grants <blue>huge damage boosts for a short time</> after using skills upon advancement. Recommended for weapons with high burst damage.

Description.SourceString: 圆月型锋刃武器，它陪伴主人完成了沿海旅行，因此得名环海。
Description.LocalizedString: A round and sharp weapon that traveled the seas with its owner.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 圆月型锋刃武器，它陪伴主人完成了沿海旅行，因此得名环海。

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the number of revolver's dodges and inflicts burn. The four-set bonus further increases damage output against burning enemies.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>技能伤害</>型武器，进阶后，可进一步提升<blue>技能伤害</>和<blue>减CD</>，且可解锁强大爆发能力
<blue>蓄力攻击</>配合其他输出手段可打出高额伤害
适合搭配技能增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Skill Damage</> weapon. Further increases <blue>Skill Damage</> and <blue>Cooldown Reduction</> upon advancement, unlocking powerful burst abilities.
 Combine <blue>Charged Shot</> with other moves to deal a high amount of damage.
 Recommended for weapons with Skill damage boosts.

Description.SourceString: 由某位科学怪人打造，测试时数值爆表，不知道火力全开情况如何。
Description.LocalizedString: Invented by a mad scientist. With its impressive test numbers, one can only imagine how powerful it might be at full power.

闪避和技能具有良好的<blue>恢复</>能力，连携可召唤电极提供后台输出
进阶后，电极的<blue>后台输出</>和<blue>恢复</>能力均可大幅提升
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Dodge and Skills provide decent <blue>healing</>. Discharge Skills summon Electrodes that provide damage output in the off-hand slot.
 Significantly increases Electrode's <blue>off-hand damage</> and <blue>healing</> upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 设计者不明，原型蓝图已流失的特制悬浮电磁炮，内部有独特的电气储蓄工艺，一旦用坏维修起来极其麻烦，但班吉斯重工的钴蓝似乎能做到。
Description.LocalizedString: Its designer is unknown. The special hovering EM Blaster's prototype's blueprint has been lost. It contains a unique electrical saving process in its interior. It's extremely troublesome to repair when it gets worn out, but Cobalt-B of Banges Tech seems to be able to do it.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the damage output of the scythe and improves its shatter ability. The four-set bonus increases the endurance of the scythe against multiple enemies.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高空中战斗输出能力，4件套提供较长时间连携增伤效果，放大连携收益
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases aerial damage output. The four-set bonus provides an increased duration of discharge damage boost discharge and increases the effectiveness of discharge.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合黑鸦冥镰的攻击距离和使用场景
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits the attack range of Scythe of the Crow and the scenes of it being used.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
充能速度快。<blue>技能和普攻</>分支具备两种模式：动心流模式兼具<blue>输出和吸血</>能力，静心流模式更偏重<blue>生存和聚怪</>能力。此外连携可提供大幅<blue>抗性</>加成
进阶后，还可获得抗性提升、主动触发幻时、降低敌人攻击力等效果
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Charges fast. <blue>Skills and Normal Attacks</> have 2 Branches: Excited Flow provides <blue>DPS and Lifesteal</>, while Silent Flow focuses on <blue>survivability and gathering enemies</>. Discharge Skills also provide significant <blue>Resistance</> boosts.
 Grants effects including Resistance Boosts, Manual Trigger Phantasia, and Enemy ATK Reduction upon advancement.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>连携伤害</>型武器，进阶后还可进一步提升<blue>连携伤害</>
释放连携后再释放技能可触发<blue>灼烧结算</>，再使用普攻可打出高额伤害
适合搭配连携增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Discharge Damage</> weapon. Further increases <blue>Discharge Damage</> upon advancement.
 Triggers <blue>Burn tally</> by casting a skill after Discharge Skill. Follow up with Normal Attack to deal a huge amount of damage.
 Recommended for weapons with Discharge damage boosts.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:

Description.SourceString: 满溢着雷霆的长枪，代号SMA1-TS00-破钧，能将储存的能量以匪夷所思的形式释放出来。由于破钧生成的电场会干扰使用者的思维，以至于常人无法驾驭。

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the healing of Absolute Zero. The four-set bonus further supports increased damage.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，从而增强治疗能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases weapon charge, which enhances healing.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加武器充能，从而增强治疗能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases weapon charge, which enhances healing.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 恢复能力极强，进阶后，可具备一定的<blue>团队辅助增伤</>能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: Has extremely strong healing abilities. Grants a certain level of <blue>Team Support Damage Boost</> upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 以精度的指针将寒冷的温度进行保持逐步稳定，最终达到疗愈。
Description.LocalizedString: Keep the cold temperature steady to heal allies.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 以精度的指针将寒冷的温度进行保持逐步稳定，最终达到疗愈。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: Keep the cold temperature steady to heal allies.

LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: Keep the cold temperature steady to heal allies.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高冰属性攻击力，增加输出，4件套强化巴尔蒙克冰域，进一步增加输出
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases frost ATK and damage output. The four-set bonus enhances Balmung Frost Domain and increases damage output.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合巴尔蒙克的攻击场景
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits the attacking scenarios of Balmung.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>闪攻伤害</>型武器，并可<blue>无视目标抗性</>
进阶后，可进一步提升<blue>闪攻</>和<blue>普攻</>的伤害，以及<blue>无视抗性</>的比例
适合搭配闪攻增伤型武器，对高抗性敌人有优势
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Dodge Attack Damage</> weapon that <blue>ignores Resistances</>.
 Further increases the damage of <blue>Dodge Attack</> and <blue>Normal Attack</> and the ratio of <blue>resistance ignored</> upon advancement.
 Recommended for weapons with Dodge Attack damage boosts. Effective against enemies with high Resistances.

Description.SourceString: 专属于赦免天使弗丽嘉的大剑与佩刀，制造时对弗丽嘉的机械躯体进行了适配。两把武器虽然并不是一体的，不过弗丽嘉将它们统称为巴尔蒙克。
Description.LocalizedString: The greatsword and the saber belonging exclusively to the Angel of Clemency, Frigg. They were adapted to Frigg's cybernetic body when they were manufactured. The two weapons are not one and the same, but Frigg refers to them collectively as Balmung.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增加闪避技收益，4件套降低怪物攻击提高队伍生存能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the effectiveness of dodge. The four-set bonus increases incoming damage reduction and team survivability.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增加V2熔驱盾的闪避能力，提高闪避收益，4件套进一步增加伤害
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases Molten Shield V2's ability to dodge and the effectiveness of dodge. The four-set bonus further increases damage.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增加V2熔驱盾的伤害，契合破盾场景，4件套增强恢复能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the damage of Molten Shield V2 and benefits shatter proficiency. The four-set bonus increases recovery.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高输出能力，契合V2熔驱盾的攻击距离
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases damage output and benefits the attack range of Molten Shield V2.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
连携可提供大量<blue>抗性加成</>和<blue>护盾</>，使用盾形态和斧形态交替普攻可获得<blue>吸血</>效果
尤其擅长对抗群体和火系攻击的敌人
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Discharge Skills provide lots of <blue>Resistance boosts</> and <blue>Shield</>. Using Normal Attack alternatively in the Shield and Axe forms grants <blue>Lifesteal</>.
 Especially effective against groups of enemies and Flame-type enemies.

Description.SourceString: 特殊工艺定制的v2系列武器之一，此为攻守一体的熔能盾斧。
Description.LocalizedString: A shield axe that belongs to the V2 weapon series, a collection of weapons forged with special techniques.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套增强晚祷驻场的伤害能力和恢复能力，4件套进一步增强晚祷驻场和生存能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus enhances the damage and recovery of Vesper while it's in the main slot. The four-set bonus further enhances Vesper's survivability while it's in the main slot.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套对重伤目标有额外增伤，契合晚祷驻场
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus gives a damage boost to grievous targets, benefitting Vesper while it's in the main slot.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
破盾能力优秀，<blue>普攻分支-瞬光</>为主要输出手段
技能和连携兼具<blue>生存</>和<blue>恢复</>能力
激活恩赐共鸣后，能够显著提升<blue>团队生存</>能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Excels at Shatter and mainly uses <blue>Shimmer</> as for damage output.
 Skills and Discharge Skills provide both <blue>survivability</> and <blue>healing</>.
 Significantly enhances the <blue>team's survivability</> upon activating Benediction Resonance.

Description.SourceString: 为某位麦德琳基金会内部人员定制的辅助型作战武器。麦德琳女士相信星寰能够得体、恰当地发挥它的真正用途。
Description.LocalizedString: A support weapon custom-made for an insider of the Maidelin Foundation. Ms. Maidelin believes that Lyra could make proper use of it.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 为某位麦德琳基金会内部人员定制的辅助型作战武器。麦德琳女士相信星寰能够得体、恰当地发挥它的真正用途。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: A support weapon custom-made for an insider of the Maidelin Foundation. Ms. Maidelin believes that Lyra could make proper use of it.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高全队生存能力，4件套提高全队的输出，攻守平衡，兼顾团队与个人
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases the team's survivability. The four-set bonus increases the team's damage output. Attack and defense are balanced. Good for team and solo play.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套增加低血量时的伤害，契合破晓的玩法
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the damage when HP is low and benefit Dawn.

 Ignores enemies' shields and deals high damage without shattering them upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 传说，这是生命之树的根须，所有生命都无法抵挡它的锋芒。

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 使魔、契约兽那一类，既然有本事授予复数女孩强大的奇异力量，自己努努力揍上去不会更有效率吗？——出于这样的考量，她决定让这位小帮手来以身作则树立个榜样。
LotteryDescription.LocalizedString: Since familiars and contract beasts can grant extraordinary powers to multiple girls, wouldn't it be more efficient for them to take direct action in combat? With this in mind, she decided to let her little helper set an example.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases DPS by increasing final damage and crit rate. The four-set bonus further increases final damage and crit rate, and grants dodge attempts.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套提高攻击力，契合四叶十字的攻击距离
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases ATK and benefits the attack range of Clover Cross.

Description.SourceString: 镜都大为流行的VR多人在线射击游戏官方——为某赛季的个人积分冠军特别设计的专属枪支。定制化的实体模型也寄送给了冠军玩家本人，但没想到的是，居然真的能像游戏中那样使用……
Description.LocalizedString: A VR multiplayer shooting game that is incredibly popular in Mirroria specially designed this exclusive gun for their top player from a certain season. The customized physical model of the gun was also sent to the player, but nobody realized it could be used just like in the game...

Description.LocalizedString: The most gnarly firearm ever created, also known as a moving turret.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases flame ATK and damage output. The four-set bonus increases flame damage and benefits the attacking scenarios of Spark.

Description.SourceString: 凛夜拜托镜都研发部门为蕾贝特制的武器，主要功能有：过家家时管家担当、早上叫蕾贝起床、为蕾贝带路……噢噢，最重要的当然是，保护蕾贝。
Description.LocalizedString: A special weapon Lin asked Mirroria R&D to make for Ruby. Its main functions include: Acting as the housekeeper in the play-house game, waking Ruby up in the morning, and leading the way for Ruby... But most importantly, protecting Ruby.

Description.SourceString: 设计者不明，原型蓝图已流失的特制悬浮电磁炮，内部有独特的电气储蓄工艺，一旦用坏维修起来极其麻烦，但班吉斯重工的钴蓝似乎能做到。
Description.LocalizedString: Its designer is unknown. The special hovering EM Blaster's prototype's blueprint has been lost. It contains a unique electrical saving process in its interior. It's extremely troublesome to repair when it gets worn out, but Cobalt-B of Banges Tech seems to be able to do it.

Description.SourceString: 专属于赦免天使弗丽嘉的大剑与佩刀，制造时对弗丽嘉的机械躯体进行了适配。两把武器虽然并不是一体的，不过弗丽嘉将它们统称为巴尔蒙克。
Description.LocalizedString: The greatsword and the saber belonging exclusively to the Angel of Clemency, Frigg. They were adapted to Frigg's cybernetic body when they were manufactured. The two weapons are not one and the same, but Frigg refers to them collectively as Balmung.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 提供暴击伤害契合格莱普尼的6阶暴击率提升并拥有不错的后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: Provide crit damage to match Gleipnir's R6 crit rate increase, and come with good off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果搭配雷队也可以使用天琅意志获得很好的后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: When in a volt group, use Tian Lang's matrix to get powerful off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果搭配影织也可能使用凛夜意志来获得后台增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: When paired with Shadoweave, use Lin's matrix to get off-hand slot damage boost.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果没有更好的意志选择也可以临时使用该意志
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: If there are no better matrices, use this one for now.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
充能速度快，连续的普攻可使目标进入<blue>沉醉状态</>，进而自身获得<blue>增伤</>能力
进阶后，可获得显著的<blue>连携增伤</>效果
适合搭配连携伤害高的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Charges fast. Consecutive Normal Attacks <blue>intoxicate</> targets and grant <blue>damage boosts</>.
 Grants effective <blue>Discharge Damage Boost</> upon advancement.
 Recommended for weapons dealing high Discharge Damage.

Description.SourceString: 能够将声波置换成攻击力量的特殊装置，当枷锁被释放，死亡电流将化作利爪，撕裂一切。
Description.LocalizedString: A special device that converts sound waves into attack. When the shackles are shattered, the currents of death become sharp claws that tear everything apart.

LotteryDescription.SourceString: 能够将声波置换成攻击力量的特殊装置，当枷锁被释放，死亡电流将化作利爪，撕裂一切。

强力的暴击输出型武器，普攻分支拥有高额<blue>暴击</>和<blue>暴击伤害</>加成
进阶后，暴击收益进一步提升
适合搭配暴击暴伤装备
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful Crit weapon. Normal Attack Branch has huge <blue>Crit</> and <blue>Crit Damage</> boosts.
 Further increases Crit upon advancement.
 Recommended for equipment providing high Crit and Crit Damage.

Description.LocalizedString: The prototype bow specially built for Rei Ayanami by the Mirroria Department of Science and Technology. Refer to the appearance and color of EVA-00. Able to fire energy arrows.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的<blue>普攻伤害</>型武器，释放技能后，驻场普攻可触发<blue>重击</>效果，造成巨额伤害，适合搭配普攻增伤型武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Normal Attack Damage</> weapon. Triggers <blue>Pummel</> with on-field normal attacks after casting a skill, dealing massive damage. Recommended for Normal Attack Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 若是被它砸一闷棍，脑瓜会立刻嗡嗡低鸣，耳边开始噼啪作响。随后眼冒金星，后脑勺鼓起一个高耸的包。
Description.LocalizedString: Getting hit by this weapon causes an immediate buzzing in the brain and crackling in the ears, followed by seeing stars and a huge bump on the back of the head.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus boosts all elemental damage in the off-hand slot and enhances Alabaster Tiger's Frost Blade ability. The four-set bonus boosts frost weapons' damage. When Alabaster Tiger is equipped, additionally increase all attack.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 3件套强化冰队的充能速度，快速速切
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The three-set bonus increases the charging speed of a frost team and makes them switch weapons quickly.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的多段<blue>技能伤害</>型武器，进阶可显著减少<blue>技能冷却</>。进入超级状态，攻击叠加<blue>状态</>后，再使用<blue>二段技能</>可打出高额伤害。适合搭配技能增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful multi-hit <blue>Skill Damage</> weapon that significantly reduces <blue>Skill Cooldown</> upon advancement. Entering Super State and stacking <blue>state</> before using the <blue>second-phase skill</> delivers very high damage. Recommended for Skill Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 摩托和大剑，这个奇妙的组合该叫什么呢？不过本来就不擅长记住名字的她，最终索性都起了个叫做噪音的名字。
Description.LocalizedString: A motorcycle and a great sword. What a peculiar combination! But since she was never good at remembering names, she eventually decided to simply call both of them Rumble.

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases flame ATK and flame damage. The four-set bonus benefits the flame team.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高暴击和暴击伤害，4件套继续提高前台和后台火队输出能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases crit and crit damage. The four-set bonus increases the flame team's main slot and off-hand slot damage output.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
技能可提供大量<blue>群体减伤</>和<blue>霸体</>效果，使用空中蓄力攻击可延长技能持续时间。释放连携技能可获得额外<blue>减伤</>效果，尤其擅长对抗群体和火系攻击的敌人。
进阶后，可提升破甲与生存能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Skills provide many <blue>Group Damage Reduction</> and <blue>Hyperbody</> effects. Using Charged Shot while airborne extends the skill's duration. Discharge Skills provide extra <blue>Damage Reduction</>. Especially effective against groups of enemies and Flame-type enemies.
 Enhances Shatter and Survivability upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 朱雀专用的伞式武具，内有各式机关。有着庞大伞身的陵光既能成为释放能量消灭敌人的利器，也能成为阻挡他人视线、隐藏自己举止的工具……
Description.LocalizedString: A parasol weapon used exclusively by Zhuque with various hidden mechanisms. Vermilion Bird's large parasol body can not only become a powerful tool to destroy enemies using energy, but also something to block the sight of others and hide the holder's demeanor...

MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
技能可提供大量<blue>群体减伤</>和<blue>霸体</>效果，使用空中蓄力攻击可延长技能持续时间。释放连携技能可获得额外<blue>减伤</>效果，尤其擅长对抗群体和火系攻击的敌人。
进阶后，可提升破甲与生存能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
Skills provide many <blue>Group Damage Reduction</> and <blue>Hyperbody</> effects. Using Charged Shot while airborne extends the skill's duration. Discharge Skills provide extra <blue>Damage Reduction</>. Especially effective against groups of enemies and Flame-type enemies.
 Enhances Shatter and Survivability upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 朱雀专用的伞式武具，内有各式机关。有着庞大伞身的陵光既能成为释放能量消灭敌人的利器，也能成为阻挡他人视线、隐藏自己举止的工具……
Description.LocalizedString: A parasol weapon used exclusively by Zhuque with various hidden mechanisms. Vermilion Bird's large parasol body can not only become a powerful tool to destroy enemies using energy, but also something to block the sight of others and hide the holder's demeanor...

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>连携伤害</>型武器，进阶后还可进一步提升<blue>连携伤害</>
释放连携后，普攻可触发<blue>静电链</>，进阶后可再触发<blue>磁暴</>，打出高额伤害
适合搭配连携增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Discharge Damage</> weapon. Further increases <blue>Discharge Damage</> upon advancement.
 Triggers <blue>Chain Static</> by using Normal Attack after Discharge Skill. Also triggers <blue>Magnetic Tempest</> upon advancement to deal a huge amount of damage.
 Recommended for weapons with Discharge damage boosts.

Description.SourceString: 海嘉德研发的可变形武器，设计精妙，性能卓著，但由于结构复杂而难以解决量产问题。「破城攻坚，一剑足矣」设计人员给予了如此评价。
Description.LocalizedString: Developed by Hykros, this transformable weapon boasts remarkable design and performance, though it's hard to mass-produce due to its complexity. "One strike is all it takes to breach a fortress."—commented its designer.

Normal Attack Branch and Skills are effective against groups of enemies.
 Grants <blue>huge damage boosts for a short time</> after using skills upon advancement. Recommended for weapons with high burst damage.

Description.SourceString: 为保证灵活和机动作战而特意打造的两把武器，无论是质量还是分量，都属上乘。「子弹穿透阴霾，利刃劈断暗夜」这是使用者内心的渴望。
Description.LocalizedString: Twin weapons crafted for agile and mobile combat, exceptional in both quality and weight. "Bullets pierce shadows, blades carve the night"—a reflection of the wielder's burning resolve.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 二件套提供物攻和火攻，四件套提供全元素增伤和最终增伤。
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus provides a physical and flame ATK, while the four-set bonus provides an all-elemental damage boost and a final damage boost.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString:
强力的<blue>普攻伤害</>型武器
长按技能可切换不同攻击形态，攻击标记目标，将触发追加攻击，造成巨额伤害
适合搭配普攻增伤型武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString:
A powerful <blue>Normal Attack Damage</> weapon.
 Hold Skill to switch between forms. Attacking marked targets triggers Pursuit Attack, dealing a huge amount of damage.
 Recommended for weapons with Normal Attack damage boosts.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 二件套提升物攻，四件套提升物理队的增伤能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: Two-set bonus: Increase physical ATK. Four-set bonus: Increase damage boost of physical weapons.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 对重伤目标伤害提高，契合明景的攻击方式
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: Increase damage dealt to grievous targets. Useful for Ming Jing's combat style.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 出色的<blue>连携增伤</>武器，具有提升前台武器充能的特殊效果。进阶后，可额外提供显著的针对<blue>连携伤害</>效果，适合搭配连携伤害高的武器。
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: An excellent <blue>Discharge Damage Boost</> weapon with a special effect that enhances the charge of main-slot weapons. Provides a significant boost to <blue>Discharge Damage</> upon advancement. Recommended for high Discharge Damage weapons.

Description.SourceString: 常人难以挥舞的巨剑，剑势凌人，锐不可当。不仅能释放惊人的破坏力，其宽阔的剑身也能带来坚如磐石的安定感。
Description.LocalizedString: An imposing and sharp greatsword that ordinary people can barely muster the strength to pick up. Its destructive power is juxtaposed by the wide blade and the sense of security it brings.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 二件套提供额外伤害手段，四件套搭配松彗时增伤效果更佳
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus provides a damage boost, while the four-set bonus further amplifies the damage boost effect when paired with Pine Comet.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高暴击和暴击伤害，4件套继续提高前台和后台火队输出能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases crit and crit damage. The four-set bonus increases the flame team's main slot and off-hand slot damage output.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 2件套提高前台输出能力，4件套提供泛用的后台能力
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: The two-set bonus increases main slot damage. The four-set provides universal off-hand slot abilities.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的<blue>连携伤害</>型武器，进阶可显著优化<blue>输出手段</>，提升<blue>输出能力</>。释放<blue>技能</>后，只需获得一定充能值，即可自动消耗并造成大量伤害。适合搭配连携增伤型的武器，与坚毅武器搭配也可显著提升坚毅职业输出能力
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Discharge Damage</> weapon. Advances to optimize <blue>damage methods</> and <blue>damage abilities</>. Casting a <blue>skill</> generates charge, automatically consumed for massive damage. Best paired with Discharge Damage Boosts or Fortitude weapons for high DPS.

Description.SourceString: 你行恶业，种恶因，得恶果，自然该受业火焚身……哈哈哈哈，我新写的台词很酷吧！哦，我打你其实是因为……我昨晚没睡好。啊对对对，我这种神经病才该被业火焚身呢！可惜，不是今天。
Description.LocalizedString: You commit evil deeds, sow bad seeds, and reap the consequences—naturally, you should be devoured by karmic fire... Haha, pretty cool, right? Oh, I hit you because... I didn't sleep well last night. Yeah, yeah, a crazy person like me should burn in karmic fire... but not today.

Description.SourceString: 规矩之间，乾坤衡定。千锻百炼，锋锐独存。不偏不倚，秋色平分。公正如云，刀下天平。

Skills provide <blue>healing</> and also <blue>clear Graying Bite</>, and enjoy extra boosts towards <blue>Bestie</>.
 Grants permanent <blue>Damage Boost Support</> upon advancement.

Description.SourceString: 使魔、契约兽那一类，既然有本事授予复数女孩强大的奇异力量，自己努努力揍上去不会更有效率吗？——出于这样的考量，她决定让这位小帮手来以身作则树立个榜样。
Description.LocalizedString: Since familiars and contract beasts can grant extraordinary powers to multiple girls, wouldn't it be more efficient for them to take direct action in combat? With this in mind, she decided to let her little helper set an example.

WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Normal Attack Damage</> weapon. Enhances <blue>DPS</> upon advancement. Grants Impact Points over time after casting a <blue>skill</>; consuming these points with a Dodge Attack deals massive damage. Recommended for Normal Attack Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 由胡萝贝设计并制造的喷气滑板，因为在户外直播中使用格外方便，所以成为了琳赛的常用装备。为此冠名的大发明家原话是——「要是遇到危险，你踩上它，哧溜一下就跑远了！」
Description.LocalizedString: A Jetboard designed and crafted by Carrot herself. Its simplicity and convenience have won Lyncis's favor. The great inventor who named this Jetboard once said, "Step on this thing, and danger won't be able to follow."

Description.SourceString: 在隐蔽、无声作战中起到重要作用的标准冷兵器，迅捷、精确、完美。
Description.LocalizedString: Fast, precise, and flawless—a standard cold weapon perfect for stealth operations when silence is key.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的<blue>普攻伤害</>型武器，分支攻击可获得<blue>霸体状态</>，输出环境优秀。释放<blue>技能</>后，可获得触腕，帮助攻击，造成大量伤害。适合搭配普攻增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Normal Attack Damage</> weapon. Branch Attack grants <blue>Hyperbody</>. Summons a tentacle after casting a <blue>skill</>, which assists attacks and deals massive damage. Recommended for Normal Attack Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 对于小朋友的玩物来说，实在是过于危险了。不可能是那孩子通过正规途径得到的东西。谁知道是用什么技术改装来的……或许是某场冒险中寻获的失落财宝吗？
Description.LocalizedString: Far too dangerous to be a child's plaything. There is no way a kid could have gotten their hands on it through honest means. Who knows what kind of tech was used to refit it... Maybe it was simply picked up somewhere off the beaten path.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的<blue>技能伤害</>型武器，释放技能后可获得<blue>协同攻击</>，一定时长后可解锁特殊闪避攻击。进阶后，特殊闪避攻击，可额外造成大量伤害，并添加压制效果。适合搭配技能增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Skill Damage</> weapon. Casting a Skill grants <blue>Coordinated Attack</>, unlocking a special Dodge Attack after a short duration. After advancement, the special Dodge Attack deals additional massive damage and inflicts a suppression effect. Recommended for Skill Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 由希望舰队的军械工厂设计并小规模生产的小型护卫机甲。通过强大的智能系统自动运行，会自行判断局势介入战斗或是进行必要辅助工作，常用于重要人物的贴身保护，平时会进入隐身状态待机。由于原料短缺而生产量极少，仅有少量极为优秀的精英人员才能用上。
Description.LocalizedString: A compact guardian mecha developed by Hope Fleet's armory. Operates autonomously with advanced AI, engaging threats or offering support as needed. Commonly used for VIP protection. Remains cloaked when idle. Issued only to top-tier operatives due to limited production.

MatrixSuitDes.SourceString: 如果没有更好的意志选择也可以临时使用该意志
MatrixSuitDes.LocalizedString: If there are no better matrices, use this one for now.

WeaponMatchDes.SourceString: 强力的<blue>技能伤害</>型武器，释放技能后可获得<blue>变身效果</>，可解锁特殊分支攻击。进阶后，特殊闪避攻击，可额外造成大量伤害。适合搭配技能增伤型的武器
WeaponMatchDes.LocalizedString: A powerful <blue>Skill Damage</> weapon. Grants <blue>Transformation Effect</> after casting a skill, unlocking a special Branch Attack. Deals additional massive damage with the special Dodge Attack upon advancement. Recommended for Skill Damage Boost weapons.

Description.SourceString: 波吕克斯不是武器，也不是拄着手杖的绅士熊娃娃，是一位受妹妹尊敬的兄长。
Description.LocalizedString: Pollux is not just a weapon, nor a gentlemanly bear doll with a cane. He is a beloved older brother to his younger sister.
